text:
mess ke saamne "chal bhai aaj drop krte hain" shayad hi kisi ka ese plan ho apne alawa , uss din bhi kya chill maara tha bhai ground pe kursi pe baith ke ,sab kuch ruk sa gya tha, piche pink floyd ,khali ground aur bc sutte ka dabba ,jisme se baar baar gin rhe the kitni bach gyi XD.
teri innocent si smile aur tere baalon ke colour ki vajah se crush tha mera tujhpe, btaio mat kisiko. 
vaise late hi mile the apan ,par last ke ek mahine main mushkil hi koi din tha jab saath baith ke bakchodi na krte ho.  aur ese hi dating tips deta rha kr mujhe. see you soon buddy!
author: Tushar  Chahar

author: Tushar  Chahar

text: abe tu... I noticed you copied my style. bc pta hi nhi chla kab assignments maangte maangte, saath main terrace pe baith ke raatein kaali krne lag gye aur ye rang birange kapde mat pehna kar meetha lgta h. I always feel sorry for you ki beardo oil lagane ke baad bhi aajtak beard nhi aayi tere XD. Always loved the way you smile in every situation and keeps *FAITH* in your heart. Saale strip ke rupee kab dega mere aur sabhu ka phone aaya tha keh rha tha pankha kharab ho toh bta dena. Jaldi hi trip maarte hain kahin dur ki.#bros4life
author: Tushar  Chahar

text:
bhai kya story rahi apan donon ki life main. bc 6 saal hogye pta hi nhi chla. hum charon ke alawa koi nhi janta uss shivam arya ko jo gaali dete hi rone lgta tha XD. 
mujhe bilkul pasand nhi tha tu starting main par dheere dheere unn sab baaton se kaafi upar uth gya main  jab dekha ki kitni similarities hain apne main, ab shayad hi koi jagah le paega teri, par bc bina btaye agra nhi jana chahie tha tujhe andar se takleeef hui thi. ab milenge toh tujhe bhi photo khinchna aur caption likhna sikha dunga chill maar! baaki life main ek baar el-clasico dekhne jroor chlenge bhai saath jaise OAT main dekhte the match aur kbhi ghr se bahar nikal ke iss side bhi aajaya kr rutvi ko akela chod ke. See you soon bro!
author: Tushar  Chahar
